nodes.text: Dark Side Squadron was the designation used by the Dark Side Elite of the Galactic Empire during at least one mission in 10 ABY. Piloting I-7 Howlrunner starfighters, the group participated in a raid on New Alderaan to abduct Jacen and Jaina Solo. They were defeated by Luke Skywalker, Kam Solusar and Empatojayos Brand. The leader of the group, Executor Xecr Nist, led Dark Side Squadron as well, flying under the callsign Dark Side One.
